<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Krishi Sarthi</title>

    <link
  href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
  rel="stylesheet"
/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">

</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/navbar') %>
  <%- include("partials/flash") %> 
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <span class="hero-badge">🌾 Smart Farming Platform</span>
        <h1>About Krishi Sarthi</h1>
        <p>Your Smart Farming Companion for Better Agriculture.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="about">
    <div class="container about-grid">

        <div class="about-text">
            <span class="section-tag">Who We Are</span>
            <h2>Empowering Every Farmer, Digitally</h2>

            <p>
                <strong>Krishi Sarthi</strong> is an intelligent agriculture platform designed
                to empower farmers with modern technology and data-driven solutions.
                Our goal is to make farming smarter, easier, and more profitable by
                providing all essential agricultural services in one place.
            </p>

            <p>
                Farmers often struggle with unpredictable weather, crop diseases,
                improper crop selection, and limited awareness of government schemes.
                Krishi Sarthi solves these challenges through easy-to-use digital tools
                that support better farming decisions.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-stats">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <h3>6+</h3>
                <p>Smart Tools</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <h3>24/7</h3>
                <p>Weather Insights</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <h3>100%</h3>
                <p>Farmer Focused</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="features">
    <div class="container">

        <span class="section-tag center">What We Offer</span>
        <h2>Our Features</h2>

        <div class="feature-grid">

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">🌱</div>
                <h3>Crop Recommendation</h3>
                <p>
                    Get crop suggestions based on soil conditions and environmental
                    factors to improve productivity and maximize yield.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">🌦</div>
                <h3>Weather Forecast</h3>
                <p>
                    Receive real-time weather updates including rainfall,
                    humidity, temperature, and wind conditions for better planning.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">🦠</div>
                <h3>Disease Detection</h3>
                <p>
                    Upload crop images to identify diseases early and receive
                    preventive measures and treatment recommendations.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">🏛</div>
                <h3>Government Schemes</h3>
                <p>
                    Stay informed about agricultural schemes, subsidies,
                    insurance, and financial support offered by the government.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">💰</div>
                <h3>Profit Prediction</h3>
                <p>
                    Estimate expected profits using crop selection,
                    production costs, and market trends.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-icon">💸</div>
                <h3>Estimated Cost</h3>
                <p>
                    Calculate farming expenses including seeds, fertilizers,
                    irrigation, pesticides, and labour costs.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="vision">
    <div class="container vision-grid">

        <div class="vision-box">
            <div class="vision-icon">🔭</div>
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <p>
                We envision a future where every farmer can make informed decisions
                using technology. Our platform aims to improve agricultural
                productivity, increase farmers' income, and promote sustainable farming.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="vision-box">
            <div class="vision-icon">🎯</div>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Empower farmers through modern technology.</li>
                <li>Promote data-driven farming decisions.</li>
                <li>Reduce crop losses through early disease detection.</li>
                <li>Improve productivity and profitability.</li>
                <li>Increase awareness of government schemes.</li>
                <li>Encourage sustainable agricultural practices.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="footer-text">
    <div class="container">

        <h2>Why Krishi Sarthi?</h2>

        <p>
            At <strong>Krishi Sarthi</strong>, we believe technology should be
            accessible to every farmer. By combining intelligent recommendations,
            accurate weather forecasts, disease detection, and financial insights,
            we strive to become a trusted digital companion for modern agriculture.
        </p>

    </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>